{"tid":1468731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲總理不同意香港出現恐怖主義的苗頭","createTime":"2019-08-13T20:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T20:31:12.000Z","uid":42767,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cb76eb2395d8d51133d93606fcec569cd997018a","tid":1468731,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:21:17.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】澳洲總理莫里森及加拿大總理杜魯多，關注香港的局勢發展，其中莫里森不同意北京形容香港的示威「出現恐怖主義苗頭」的言論。<br />\n<br />\n另外，加拿大總理杜魯多亦對香港的局勢表示擔憂，認為有必要令事情降溫，呼籲展開對話，又敦促中國政府要非常小心和以尊重方式，處理港人的關注。他又表示，政府會確保加拿大在香港的利益，目前大約有三十萬加拿大公民在本港居住。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=359013&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D359013%26refer%3D&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=21ebb66c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D359013%26refer%3D&h=225bf34f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=359013&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"9393a95df2dcfa7f844865c024456ffaf76c8be3","tid":1468731,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:22:38.000Z","msg":"有喎<br />\n六一二<br />\n七二一<br />\n七二八<br />\n八一一<br />\n全部都係恐怖主義喎"},{"pid":"f5e8e3b2ec70095676bc03b9acca42998bde778c","tid":1468731,"uid":261913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:22:42.000Z","msg":"30萬要幾多轉飛機先飛得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb88b2de1654e22e31057d2945ae081ff179933","tid":1468731,"uid":263820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:23:48.000Z","msg":"有無人可以話我知突然全世界都出聲係咩事.."},{"pid":"2696b51fdc9288dc763c374ab6da98e187321f41","tid":1468731,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5e8e3b2ec70095676bc03b9acca42998bde778c","tid":1468731,"uid":261913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:22:42.000